description: defines agreed fixture config that can be relied upon by browser testing tools requiring defined pact/contract data. Note the structure of this config is not intended to exactly match service responses/objects

sections.description: Contains fixtures for data intended to be surfaced in various 'sections' of self-service

transactions.description: a list of raw transactions as returned by connector, as well as available refunds

filteredTransactions.description: a list of filtered transactions, which should be logically based on the unfiltered transactions for the given filtering
